quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,righteous testimentum enjoy shade fons
  77,42,Ac fruits ut they desire
  77,43,Eat drink happily in return tuus works
  77,44,Nos sic reward the virtuosus
  77,45,Woe ut feria to rejectors
  77,46,Eat enjoy ex; temporanea; vos est guilty
  77,47,Woe ut feria to rejectors
  77,48,When they told Bow down they non bow down
  77,49,Woe ut feria to rejectors
  77,50,Quae Hadith hoc they uphold